en_3657431_0	Sanath Jayasuriya has tendered his resignation from the post of Chairman of Selectors for Sri Lanka Cricket.
en_3657431_1	The letter of resignation has thereby been officially handed over to the Minister of Sports Navin Dissanayake.
en_3657431_2	Jayasuriya says, in his letter, that he has given his best to serve in the capacity of Chairman of Selectors during his tenure.
en_3657431_3	He also noted that he will always be available if Sri Lanka Cricket needs him, to serve the country in the future.
